{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 93570, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 15668, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这个情况学校应该也会允许休学？", "timestamp": 1594034055, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 93590, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 15668, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 应该允许。", "timestamp": 1594034242, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 93605, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 15668, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "但是赚的那点钱也不够啊", "timestamp": 1594034449, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 93607, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 15668, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我也觉得 首先应该尽自己最大努力吧", "timestamp": 1594034568, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 93608, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 15668, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 所以躺平靠别人吗……", "timestamp": 1594034617, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 93609, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 15668, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "怎么说 继续读下去会比直接工作有更好的前途 现在有这种既能给父母治病又能保证自己前途的方法 谁不心动呢？", "timestamp": 1594034621, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 93611, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 15668, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 赚钱不够发起众筹和还没赚钱就发起众筹我感觉不太一样。。", "timestamp": 1594034652, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 93645, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 15668, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "带物理竞赛应该很赚的...无论如何，祝早日康复🙏", "timestamp": 1594035138, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 93646, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 15668, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 可能是她情况紧急，医药费马上耗光了", "timestamp": 1594035148, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 93664, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 15668, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "物理系直博的补助应该在每月5-7k范围，这个同学直博的实验室也是物理系少有的偏应用的与产业界对接的实验室，好像大老板前两年退休全职开公司了？能博士毕业的话就业应该挺乐观。。", "timestamp": 1594035447, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 93871, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 15668, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "那个学生父母都是癌症，疾病，你让她放弃学位挣钱短时间内也是杯水车薪，哪怕她现在出去一个月能挣两万，你算算顶什么用？你又怎么知道她没有兼职努力赚钱多方筹款而且躺平等捐？最后，异地处之，你真的会选择放弃学业？？？", "timestamp": 1594038269, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 93967, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 15668, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 易x", "timestamp": 1594038850, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 93998, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 15668, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "突然想起最好的我们里面，余淮因为要照顾母亲放弃上清华而选择读本地一所高校", "timestamp": 1594039083, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 10, "pid": 15668, "reply": 13, "tag": null, "text": "如果是我的话我会放弃直博，抓紧挣钱，毕竟博士是一个时间成本极高的学位，并且什么时候毕业具有不确定性。物理系本科出去，去课外辅导机构，应该还是能获得可观的收入。只要人在，就有希望，以后继续学业也不是不可能的事情。\n当然我这也是慨他人之慷，一家之言。", "timestamp": 1594034024, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782591, "url": "", "vote": {}}}